Dr. Geo is an interactive geometry software.

-----------------------
Installing Dependecies:
-----------------------
You must first install certain dependencies before you can run the software.
Install them as following if you are using Ubuntu/Debian distros:

sudo apt-get install autogen autotools-dev intltool libtool libgtk-3-dev

--------------------------
Run following commands to
configure and install:
--------------------------
glib-gettextize
intltoolize --force
libtoolize
aclocal
autoheader
automake --add-missing
autoconf
./configure
make
sudo make install

---------------
To run Dr. Geo:
---------------
drgeo
